metadata.name: Space Yacht HOKULANI - Red Planet 1 of 200
metadata.description:
Space Voyager - HOKULANI - Streamliner class. 

Space vessel Intended for flights based on quantum jumps at short and medium distances.

Luxury interplanetary vehicles based on advanced technology for space travel in the XXII century.
Designed by The Exponential corp. in 2170 - it is capable of carrying 150 passengers and a substantial amount of cargo

Passengers benefit from the most comfortable space travel conditions possible with a living area of 2000 mÂ² and the best hyper sleep pods in its class.

1st edition set of 200
